01:37:59,840 --> 01:38:02,331
It was the right hand of a
convicted murderer...

943
01:38:02,443 --> 01:38:04,104
cut off while his neck
was still in the noose.

944
01:38:04,211 --> 01:38:07,305
Or so Margaret believed.

945
01:38:07,414 --> 01:38:10,611
- Black magic.
- Black, white, what difference does it make?

946
01:38:10,718 --> 01:38:12,709
- Margaret was always...
- Evil.

947
01:38:12,820 --> 01:38:14,981
Evil is a dunghill, Mr. Angel.

948
01:38:15,089 --> 01:38:17,887
Everyone gets on his own and
speaks out about someone else's.

949
01:38:17,992 --> 01:38:22,019
Margaret wasn't evil.
She was a strange kid, though.

950
01:38:22,129 --> 01:38:24,461
She was into tarot cards
before she could read.

951
01:38:24,565 --> 01:38:26,863
Who got her started?

952
01:38:26,967 --> 01:38:29,265
Some maid, governess...
who knows?

953
01:38:29,370 --> 01:38:32,806
Some maid, some governess... Everything
you tell me is a crock of shit!

954
01:38:32,907 --> 01:38:37,310
You're the one that got her started!
You're the fuckin' devil worshipper!

955
01:38:37,411 --> 01:38:39,675
The prince of darkness
protects the powerful.

956
01:38:39,780 --> 01:38:42,806
- That's a crock of shit!
- I can't help it if you don't believe.

957
01:38:42,917 --> 01:38:47,445
You come straight with me, you slimebag,
or I'll save this state an execution.

958
01:38:47,554 --> 01:38:50,921
I introduced Johnny Favorite
to my daughter. He was very powerful.

959
01:38:51,025 --> 01:38:53,892
I once watched him conjure up
"Lucifuge" in my living room.

960
01:38:53,994 --> 01:38:55,689
He was in it much deeper than me.

961
01:38:55,796 --> 01:38:58,959
He made a pact with Satan.
He sold his soul.

962
01:38:59,066 --> 01:39:00,795
You expect me to swallow that?

963
01:39:00,901 --> 01:39:02,061
Swallow it. Spit it out.
I don't give a damn.

964
01:39:02,169 --> 01:39:06,333
That's a crock of shit, you
lying, old, fucking motherfucker!

965
01:39:06,440 --> 01:39:09,568
- He sold his soul for stardom.
- For stardom? Are you...

966
01:39:09,677 --> 01:39:13,340
- That's a crock of shit!
- Satan rose from the depth.

967
01:39:13,447 --> 01:39:16,610
It was magnificent, except he thought
he could outwit the prince of darkness.

968
01:39:16,717 --> 01:39:20,278
Johnny sold his soul. Then when he
made it big, he tried to duck out of it.

969
01:39:20,387 --> 01:39:22,252
That's a crock of shit!

970
01:39:22,356 --> 01:39:25,189
Johnny came across an obscure rite
in an ancient manuscript.

971
01:39:25,292 --> 01:39:28,489
- He needed a victim his own age.
- Why?

972
01:39:28,595 --> 01:39:32,895
To steal their soul. So Toots and Johnny
picked up a young soldier.

973
01:39:33,000 --> 01:39:33,796
Who?

974
01:39:33,901 --> 01:39:36,836
Just a soldier celebrating New
Year's eve in Times Square.

975
01:39:36,937 --> 01:39:39,497
- Who was this soldier?
- They took him back to Johnny's hotel.

976
01:39:39,606 --> 01:39:42,973
- That's where the ceremony took place.
- What ceremony?

977
01:39:43,077 --> 01:39:45,477
The boy was bound naked
on a rubber mat.

978
01:39:45,579 --> 01:39:48,707
There were complicated incantations
and stuff in Latin and Greek.

979
01:39:48,816 --> 01:39:51,216
A pentacle was branded
on his chest.

980
01:39:51,318 --> 01:39:55,118
Margaret handed Johnny a virgin dagger
and he sliced the boy clean open.

981
01:39:55,222 --> 01:39:57,713
And he ate his heart.

982
01:39:57,825 --> 01:40:01,022
He cut it out so quickly the heart was
still beating when he wolfed it down.

983
01:40:01,128 --> 01:40:05,121
Johnny's plan was to drop out
and resurface as the soldier.

984
01:40:05,232 --> 01:40:07,962
But before he could work
things out, he was drafted.

985
01:40:08,068 --> 01:40:11,094
Then Johnny was injured, sent home
without even knowing who he was.

986
01:40:11,205 --> 01:40:13,799
Who was that boy?

987
01:40:13,907 --> 01:40:19,174
Only Johnny knew. He sealed the dog tags
in a vase and gave it to Margaret.

988
01:40:19,279 --> 01:40:21,873
It was Margaret's plan
to drop him off in Times Square.

989
01:40:21,982 --> 01:40:25,884
That would be the last place that
he'd remember before it happened.

990
01:40:29,289 --> 01:40:32,019
He needed a victim...
someone his own age...

991
01:40:35,295 --> 01:40:38,423
to steal their soul.

992
01:40:38,532 --> 01:40:43,094
And he sliced the boy
clean open and he ate his heart.

993
01:40:43,203 --> 01:40:46,468
Who was the boy?

994
01:40:46,573 --> 01:40:51,033
Johnny's plan was to drop out
and resurface as the soldier.

995
01:40:51,145 --> 01:40:53,272
Or maybe he gained possession
of the guy's soul.

996
01:40:53,380 --> 01:40:54,870
He still looked like Johnny to me.

997
01:41:04,625 --> 01:41:06,525
Oh, shit!

998
01:43:10,717 --> 01:43:12,617
No!

999
01:43:17,724 --> 01:43:20,955
I know who I am!
I know who I am!

1000
01:43:40,214 --> 01:43:44,048
Alas.

1001
01:43:44,151 --> 01:43:48,747
How terrible is wisdom when it brings
no profit to the wise, Johnny.

1002
01:43:50,424 --> 01:43:52,551
Louis Cyphre.

1003
01:43:54,127 --> 01:43:57,255
Lucifer.

1004
01:43:57,364 --> 01:44:00,458
Even your name
is a dime-store joke.

1005
01:44:00,567 --> 01:44:04,697
Mephistopheles is such
a mouthful in Manhattan, Johnny.

1006
01:44:04,805 --> 01:44:08,036
You think posing as the devil...

1007
01:44:08,141 --> 01:44:11,907
just 'cause it scared some
superstitious old guitar player...

1008
01:44:12,012 --> 01:44:15,709
and that witch
and that nutty old man...

1009
01:44:15,816 --> 01:44:17,943
You think it's gonna scare me?

1010
01:44:18,051 --> 01:44:21,509
It ain't, 'cause I know who I am.

1011
01:44:21,622 --> 01:44:25,558
And you killed them,
and you're tryin' to pin it on me.

1012
01:44:25,659 --> 01:44:28,787
And I know who I am.

1013
01:44:28,895 --> 01:44:32,456
If I had cloven hoofs and a pointed
tail, would you be more convinced?

1014
01:44:34,401 --> 01:44:36,562
You're crazy.

1015
01:44:36,670 --> 01:44:39,969
I know who I am.
You're trying to frame me.

1016
01:44:40,073 --> 01:44:43,406
You're trying to frame me.
Cyphre, I know who I am.

1017
01:44:43,510 --> 01:44:46,411
You murdered them people.
I never killed nobody.

1018
01:44:46,513 --> 01:44:49,778
I didn't kill Fowler...

1019
01:44:49,883 --> 01:44:51,783
and...

1020
01:44:51,885 --> 01:44:54,149
and I didn't kill Toots...

1021
01:44:54,254 --> 01:44:57,519
and I didn't kill Margaret
and I didn't kill Krusemark.

1022
01:44:57,624 --> 01:45:00,149
I didn't kill no one.

1023
01:45:00,260 --> 01:45:03,593
- I'm afraid you did, Johnny.
- My name's not Johnny.

1024
01:45:03,697 --> 01:45:05,790
All killed by your own hand.

1025
01:45:05,899 --> 01:45:08,527
Guided by me, naturally.

1026
01:45:08,635 --> 01:45:12,162
Frankly, you were doomed from the moment
you slit that young boy in half.

1027
01:45:12,272 --> 01:45:14,536
And Johnny...

1028
01:45:14,641 --> 01:45:19,169
for 12 years you've been living on
borrowed time in another man's memories.

1029
01:45:22,749 --> 01:45:25,445
Hey, I'm gonna tell Winesap,
'cause he knows.

1030
01:45:25,552 --> 01:45:28,885
Winesap? Well, he's dead.

1031
01:45:28,989 --> 01:45:30,047
Nasty accident.

1032
01:45:32,292 --> 01:45:36,194
Don't worry. No one will mourn
one less lawyer in the world.

1033
01:45:36,296 --> 01:45:39,527
There's death everywhere
these days, Johnny.

1034
01:45:39,633 --> 01:45:44,127
But what gives human life
its worth anyway?

1035
01:45:44,237 --> 01:45:47,832
Because someone loves it or hates it?

1036
01:45:47,941 --> 01:45:51,934
The flesh is weak, Johnny.
Only the soul is immortal.

1037
01:45:57,617 --> 01:46:00,211
And yours belongs to me.

1038
01:46:04,791 --> 01:46:06,918
I know who I am.

1039
01:46:10,864 --> 01:46:14,265
That's it, Johnny.
Take a good look.

1040
01:46:15,335 --> 01:46:17,530
However cleverly you
sneak up on a mirror...

1041
01:46:17,637 --> 01:46:20,538
your reflection always
looks you straight in the eye.

1042
01:46:20,640 --> 01:46:23,006
I know who I am!

1043
01:46:32,519 --> 01:46:34,077
- Well...
- Girl of my dreams

1044
01:46:34,187 --> 01:46:36,849
I love you

1045
01:46:36,957 --> 01:46:41,394
Honest, I do

1046
01:46:41,495 --> 01:46:48,958
You are so sweet

1047
01:46:50,203 --> 01:46:53,468
If I could just
hold your charms

1048
01:46:53,573 --> 01:46:58,237
- I know who I am!
- Again in my arms

1049
01:46:59,579 --> 01:47:03,140
Then life would be

1050
01:47:03,250 --> 01:47:07,414
Complete

1051
01:47:07,521 --> 01:47:11,423
Since you've been gone, dear

1052
01:47:12,692 --> 01:47:15,923
Life don't seem the same

1053
01:47:17,264 --> 01:47:20,461
Please come back

1054
01:47:20,567 --> 01:47:24,128
With me

1055
01:47:25,272 --> 01:47:29,572
And after all's said and done

1056
01:47:29,676 --> 01:47:34,511
There's only one

1057
01:47:34,614 --> 01:47:38,380
Girl of my dreams

1058
01:47:38,485 --> 01:47:41,750
That's you

1059
01:48:08,014 --> 01:48:09,538
Why'd you come back?

1060
01:48:19,893 --> 01:48:21,793
I live here.

1061
01:48:23,597 --> 01:48:25,656
Who is she?

1062
01:48:27,701 --> 01:48:30,727
She ain't "Angel, Harold."

1063
01:48:33,440 --> 01:48:35,738
She's my daughter.

1064
01:48:35,842 --> 01:48:38,538
Bullshit. Who is she?

1065
01:48:39,946 --> 01:48:43,382
She's Epiphany Proudfoot.

1066
01:48:43,483 --> 01:48:45,974
She stayed here for a little while.

1067
01:48:48,655 --> 01:48:50,850
Long enough for you
to kill her, right?

1068
01:48:50,957 --> 01:48:53,084
Unless that ain't your gun
up her snatch.

1069
01:49:10,410 --> 01:49:12,605
You're gonna burn for this, Angel.

1070
01:49:15,682 --> 01:49:17,877
I know.

1071
01:49:19,686 --> 01:49:21,586
In hell.

1072
01:50:02,062 --> 01:50:05,429
Subtitled By
Captions, Inc. Los Angeles

1073
01:52:51,131 --> 01:52:53,031
Harry.

1074
01:52:53,133 --> 01:52:55,033
Johnny.

